ed a question of one of the sisters, certain to cause debate among those surrounding her. A simple question really. One of Amazon tribal customs of something Hope would later forget. Their breif distraction was all the time Hope needed to pocket the stone. The next rune in her quest for nine. The Amazons asked her if she would stay for the nights gathering but she felt the need to excuse herself. She paid open respects to the fallen Amazon sister. The Amazons of the Sacred Circle wished Hope well as she travelled to her next destination.... the Amazons of Sarmatia.....<br>
